<div class="text_cell_render border-box-sizing rendered_html">
  <h2 id="The-following-loop-is-used-for-opening-each-downloaded-file,-checking-whether-the-filename-in-<SEC-DOCUMENT>-is-the-same-as-that-given-in-the-sec-dataframe-and,-if-different,-then-fixing-to-correct-(and-shorter)-filename">
    The following loop is used for opening each downloaded file, checking whether the filename in <SEC-DOCUMENT> is the same as that given in the sec dataframe and, if different, then fixing to correct (and shorter) filename<a class="anchor-link" href="#The-following-loop-is-used-for-opening-each-downloaded-file,-checking-whether-the-filename-in-<SEC-DOCUMENT>-is-the-same-as-that-given-in-the-sec-dataframe-and,-if-different,-then-fixing-to-correct-(and-shorter)-filename">&#182;</a>
  </h2>
</div>

<div class="cell border-box-sizing code_cell vbox">
  <div class="input hbox">
    <div class="input_area box-flex1">
      <div class="highlight">
        <pre><span class="n">start</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">&#39;&lt;sec-document&gt;&#39;</span>
<span class="n">end</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">&#39;:&#39;</span> 
<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">index</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">row</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">sec</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">iterrows</span><span class="p">():</span> 
    <span class="k">print</span> <span class="s">&#39;index&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">index</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">row</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">&#39;Form Type&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span>
    <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">row</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">&#39;Form Type&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="s">&#39;4&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="n">idx</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">index</span>            <span class="c">### THIS NEEDS TO COME HERE (NOT BEFORE &#39;IF&#39; STATEMENT) OR ELSE IT WILL MESS UP THE ROW COPYING</span>
        <span class="n">saved_fname</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">&#39;Form 4 -index-&#39;</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">idx</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="s">&#39; &#39;</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">row</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">&#39;Filename&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">replace</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#39;/&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="s">&#39;-&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">replace</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#39;.txt&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="s">&#39;.htm&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
        
        <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">root</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">dirs</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">filenames</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">os</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">walk</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">indir</span><span class="p">):</span>
            <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">f</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">filenames</span><span class="p">:</span>
                <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">f</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="n">saved_fname</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="c">#&#39;8-K-index-10008-edgar-data-1532750-0001193125-14-187431.htm&#39;:</span>
                    <span class="c">#print "IT&#39;S A MATCH!"</span>
                    <span class="nb">file</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">indir</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="s">&#39;/&#39;</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">f</span>
                    <span class="n">data</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">open</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">os</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">path</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">join</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">root</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">f</span><span class="p">),</span> <span class="s">&#39;r&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">read</span><span class="p">()</span>
                    <span class="n">sec_filename</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">split</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">start</span><span class="p">))[</span><span class="mi"></span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">split</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">end</span><span class="p">)[</span><span class="mi"></span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">replace</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#39;&lt;SEC-DOCUMENT&gt;&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="s">&#39;&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
                    <span class="c">#print saved_fname</span>
                    <span class="c">#print &#39;sec_filename&#39;, sec_filename #, &#39;\n&#39;</span>
                    <span class="n">svd_filename</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">saved_fname</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">split</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#39;-&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">)[</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">replace</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#39;htm&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">&#39;txt&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
                    <span class="c">#print &#39;svd_filename&#39;, svd_filename</span>
                    <span class="n">old_name</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">indir</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="s">&#39;/&#39;</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">saved_fname</span> 
                    <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">sec_filename</span> <span class="o">!=</span> <span class="n">svd_filename</span> <span class="ow">and</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">sec_filename</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="mi">10</span> <span class="ow">and</span> <span class="n">os</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">stat</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">indir</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="s">&#39;/&#39;</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">saved_fname</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">st_size</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="mi"></span><span class="p">:</span>
                        <span class="k">print</span> <span class="s">&#39;filename is incorrect!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!&#39;</span>
                        <span class="k">print</span> <span class="s">&#39;saving as: &#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">indir</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="s">&#39;/&#39;</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">sec_filename</span>
                        <span class="n">os</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">rename</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">old_name</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">indir</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="s">&#39;/&#39;</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">sec_filename</span><span class="p">)</span>
                    <span class="k">elif</span> <span class="n">sec_filename</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="n">svd_filename</span><span class="p">:</span>
                        <span class="k">print</span> <span class="s">&#39;SAME FILENAME&#39;</span>
                        <span class="c">#print &#39;saving as: &#39;, indir+&#39;/&#39;+svd_filename                        </span>
                        <span class="c">#os.rename(old_name, indir+&#39;/&#39;+svd_filename)</span>
                    <span class="k">elif</span> <span class="n">sec_filename</span> <span class="o">!=</span> <span class="n">svd_filename</span> <span class="ow">and</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">sec_filename</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="mi">10</span><span class="p">:</span>
                        <span class="k">print</span> <span class="s">&#39;sec_filename&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">sec_filename</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">"THE FILENAME IS SO SHORT............................."</span>
                    <span class="k">elif</span> <span class="n">os</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">stat</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">indir</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="s">&#39;/&#39;</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">saved_fname</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">st_size</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">:</span>
                        <span class="k">print</span> <span class="s">&#39;saved_fname&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">saved_fname</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">&#39;FILESIZE ZERO&#39;</span>
                    <span class="c">#print old_name</span>
                    <span class="c">#os.rename(old_name, indir+&#39;/&#39;+sec_filename)</span>

    <span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="k">print</span> <span class="s">&#39;NOT FORM 4, THIS IS A FORM&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">row</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">&#39;Form Type&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span>
</pre>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3 id="I-think-this-is-the-original-loop-used-for-downloading-the-files">
    I think this is the original loop used for downloading the files<a class="anchor-link" href="#I-think-this-is-the-original-loop-used-for-downloading-the-files">&#182;</a>
  </h3>
</div>

<div class="cell border-box-sizing code_cell vbox">
  <div class="input hbox">
    <div class="input_area box-flex1">
      <div class="highlight">
        <pre><span class="n">url_prefix</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">&#39;ftp://ftp.sec.gov/&#39;</span>
<span class="c">##### STARTED DOWNLOADING TEXT FILES AT INDEX #8541</span>
<span class="c">#for index, row in sec[8541:].iterrows():</span>
<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">index</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">row</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">sec</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">17147</span><span class="p">:]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">iterrows</span><span class="p">():</span>
<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">index</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">row</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">sec</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">17147</span><span class="p">:]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">iterrows</span><span class="p">():</span>
    <span class="n">idx</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">index</span>
    <span class="k">print</span> <span class="s">&#39;index&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">index</span>   <span class="c">#, row</span>
    <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">row</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">&#39;Form Type&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="s">&#39;4&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="n">time</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">sleep</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="n">data</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">urllib2</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">urlopen</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">file_url</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">read</span><span class="p">()</span>
        <span class="c">#print row[&#39;Filename&#39;]    </span>
        <span class="n">file_url</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">url_prefix</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">row</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">&#39;Filename&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span>        
        <span class="n">new_fname</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">&#39;Form 4 -index-&#39;</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">index</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="s">&#39; &#39;</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">row</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">&#39;Filename&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">replace</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#39;/&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="s">&#39;-&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">replace</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#39;.txt&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="s">&#39;.htm&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="c">#print &#39;new_fname&#39;, new_fname</span>
        <span class="n">old_fname</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">new_fname</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">replace</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#39;-&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="s">&#39;/&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">replace</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#39;.htm&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="s">&#39;.txt&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="c">#print &#39;old_fname&#39;, old_fname</span>
        <span class="n">old_fname_v2</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">old_fname</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">split</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#39; &#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="c">#print old_fname_v2[3]</span>
        <span class="c">#if row[&#39;Filename&#39;] == old_fname_v2[3]:</span>
        <span class="c">#    print &#39;match&#39;</span>
        <span class="nb">file</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">&#39;SEC filings/4/</span><span class="si">%s</span><span class="s">&#39;</span> <span class="o">%</span> <span class="n">new_fname</span>

        <span class="k">with</span> <span class="nb">open</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">file</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">&#39;w&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">f</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">f</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">write</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="n">f</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">()</span>
        
</pre>
